"""backend/tests/test_auto_quant.py — Comprehensive Auto-Quant Factory Test Suite

Covers all five mandated verification areas:

  §1  generator.py  — produces a syntax-error-free, structurally correct
                      strategy that uses CategoricalParameter for all three
                      entry-logic options (macd_cross, rsi_oversold, bb_breakout).

  §2  State-machine — Stages 1-7 transition correctly through the pipeline;
                      statuses are set, passed data is attached, final state
                      is "completed" with all 7 stages "passed".

  §3  Self-Healing  — retry_count increments on each OOS overfit signal,
                      per-retry parameter overrides are applied in order,
                      and the pipeline hard-fails after exhausting max_retries.

  §4  Monte Carlo gate — run_monte_carlo() math is correct; Stage 6 raises a
                         hard failure when the simulated p95 drawdown >= 35%.

  §5  API endpoints — GET /runs and GET/POST /download return 200 OK with
                      valid content and never 500.

Run from the project root:
    pytest backend/tests/test_auto_quant.py -v
"""

from __future__ import annotations

